metadata.name: All I could see was her mouth
metadata.description:
All I could see was her mouth, a perfect red bow set against the redness. 

I was mesmerized, unable to look away from the beauty before me. 

But as she stepped closer, I realized that her mouth was not the only thing that was breathtaking - her entire being radiated a captivating charm that left me speechless. I was lost in her presence, unable to resist her allure.

Technique: AI mashup of images created with AI and creative coding.
Resolution: 4096 x 6144
